1000
01:02:53,061 --> 01:02:55,393
Yeah!

1001
01:02:55,397 --> 01:02:57,559
Who is it they're shooting?
What are you talking about?

1002
01:02:57,565 --> 01:02:59,897
Running Deer couldn't even
kill a deer and feed

1003
01:02:59,901 --> 01:03:01,483
his starving family.

1004
01:03:01,486 --> 01:03:03,272
Right!

1005
01:03:03,280 --> 01:03:04,691
Indians have to go hungry.

1006
01:03:06,283 --> 01:03:09,071
But these trophy hunters,
they come in here and they do

1007
