Yeah!

1010
01:03:16,251 --> 01:03:18,208
All right.

1011
01:03:18,211 --> 01:03:20,373
The question is, what are we
going to do about it.

1012
01:03:20,380 --> 01:03:21,711
Let's run them out.

1013
01:03:24,175 --> 01:03:26,587
I think we should take
some cameras and go down

