in to the newspaper.

1016
01:03:31,016 --> 01:03:34,509
Hey. Better than that,
better than that.

1017
01:03:34,519 --> 01:03:36,430
Let's send them
to their wives.

1018
01:03:36,438 --> 01:03:39,271
--Got a right to hunt
on Indian land.

1019
01:03:41,526 --> 01:03:44,359
That's what the law students
were trying to tell you before.

1020
01:03:44,362 --> 01:03:46,569
That's no longer Indian land.

1021
01:03:46,573 --> 01:03:49,281
That's part of the reservation
that they've been quietly

1022
01:03:49,284 --> 01:03:51,571
terminating for our own good.

1023
01:03:53,204 --> 01:03:56,037
Not to me it isn't.

1024
01:03:56,041 --> 01:03:57,873
What is that supposed to mean?

1025
01:03:57,876 --> 01:03:59,958
I never voted for termination.

1026
01:04:00,462 --> 01:04:03,079
Did anybody in this room
ever vote for termination?

1027
01:04:03,548 --> 01:04:05,710
No!

1028
01:04:05,717 --> 01:04:07,253
Do you know
of any tribal member

1029
01:04:07,260 --> 01:04:09,547
who knowingly voted
for termination?

1030
01:04:09,554 --> 01:04:11,511
No!

1031
01:04:12,057 --> 01:04:14,765
Then to me they're still
illegally on Indian land

1032
01:04:14,768 --> 01:04:17,476
and this tribal council has
the authority to arrest them

1033
01:04:17,479 --> 01:04:18,765
and drive them out.

1034
01:04:20,190 --> 01:04:22,602
What do you mean, arrest them?

1035
01:04:22,609 --> 01:04:23,770
Who's gonna do it?

1036
01:04:23,777 --> 01:04:26,360
I will. The tribal police.

1037
01:04:26,905 --> 01:04:30,068
Or anyone in this room who is
man enough to go with me.

1038
01:04:30,075 --> 01:04:31,782
Or tell me something.

1039
01:04:31,785 --> 01:04:34,243
Are you afraid to stand up to
the white man even when he's

1040
01:04:34,245 --> 01:04:36,236
shooting at your wives
and your children?

1041
01:04:36,247 --> 01:04:37,908
No!

1042
01:04:41,503 --> 01:04:44,291
Me and my rifle can be
any place you say

1043
01:04:44,297 --> 01:04:46,584
within half an hour.

1044
01:04:49,844 --> 01:04:52,632
Now, they're calling
this the international

1045
