symposium on the law.

1046
01:04:54,099 --> 01:04:56,557
And the American Indian
legal rights--

1047
01:04:56,559 --> 01:04:58,846
And let me tell
you guys something.

1048
01:04:58,853 --> 01:05:01,641
The real purpose of this is to
make it look like everybody's

1049
01:05:01,648 --> 01:05:02,934
stealing from the Indians.

1050
01:05:02,941 --> 01:05:04,431
Oh, come on, Posner.

1051
01:05:04,442 --> 01:05:07,935
I've handled dozens of land
sales of Indians and even I

1052
01:05:07,946 --> 01:05:10,608
don't know what
termination is. Do you?

1053
01:05:10,615 --> 01:05:14,279
Look, these radical Indians are
taking payoffs on all sides.

1054
01:05:14,285 --> 01:05:17,118
Who cares? As long as they
don't terminate my lease.

1055
01:05:17,122 --> 01:05:19,784
I've only got 92 more years
for it to run.

1056
01:05:22,001 --> 01:05:24,208
Well, you sure as hell better
hope that conference

1057
01:05:24,212 --> 01:05:25,452
never takes place.

1058
01:05:25,463 --> 01:05:28,330
Because if it does, we're all
in for a lot of surprises.

1059
01:06:17,182 --> 01:06:20,800
I order you to drop your guns.

1060
01:06:29,360 --> 01:06:32,022
You sentence our brother
Running Deer to jail

1061
01:06:32,030 --> 01:06:35,022
for killing a deer to feed
his starving children,

1062
01:06:35,033 --> 01:06:38,697
and yet you dare to come here
and do this?

1063
01:06:40,955 --> 01:06:42,787
What, do you call this sport?

1064
01:06:42,790 --> 01:06:45,202
I was wrong.

1065
01:06:45,210 --> 01:06:47,702
I'll correct that injustice
to the Indian.

1066
01:06:47,712 --> 01:06:48,622
Well, tell me.

1067
01:06:48,630 --> 01:06:49,836
Just how are you
going to do that?

1068
01:06:50,381 --> 01:06:53,339
He's already spent ten days
rotting in your lousy jail

1069
01:06:53,343 --> 01:06:54,549
like a caged animal.

1070
01:06:54,552 --> 01:06:57,340
I'll give Running Deer a job.
A good job.

1071
01:06:58,056 --> 01:07:00,047
More money than he could
possibly earn.

1072
01:07:00,058 --> 01:07:01,469
Because he's an Indian?

1073
01:07:01,809 --> 01:07:03,595
And you've got one pay scale
for your whites and one

1074
01:07:03,603 --> 01:07:04,934
for your Indians?

1075
01:07:04,938 --> 01:07:08,056
Aw, come on, now.
Don't be childish.

1076
01:07:08,066 --> 01:07:09,556
All of you.

1077
01:07:09,567 --> 01:07:13,231
You are all illegally
trespassing on Indian land

