So I'm going to ask you
one small favor.

2238
02:23:32,562 --> 02:23:38,148
Can you give Danny his chance
to be a big guy?

2239
02:23:38,151 --> 02:23:41,644
And I hope to God he doesn't
turn out like some of you.

2240
