Thank you.

2261
02:25:06,907 --> 02:25:09,945
I'm well aware of that,
but ask for them anyway.

2262
02:25:09,951 --> 02:25:13,239
I don't give a damn,
we need some help.

2263
02:25:13,246 --> 02:25:15,487
All right.

2264
02:25:15,498 --> 02:25:16,784
Well, they won't pull out.

2265
02:25:16,791 --> 02:25:18,907
We're trying to ask
for federal marshals.

2266
02:25:18,919 --> 02:25:20,956
Has anybody gotten through
to the governor yet?

2267
02:25:20,962 --> 02:25:23,078
Oh, Jean, I've been trying
to get him all afternoon.

2268
02:25:23,089 --> 02:25:25,626
No, he doesn't have time
for a phone call.

2269
02:25:25,634 --> 02:25:28,626
But look at him. He's acting
like the archangel Gabriel.

2270
02:25:28,637 --> 02:25:31,299
So I pledge to you

2271
02:25:31,306 --> 02:25:33,422
that while we will never
provoke any confrontation--

2272
02:25:33,433 --> 02:25:36,141
- Damn you liar.
- ...we will never surrender

2273
02:25:36,144 --> 02:25:40,934
one square foot of this state
to any lawless anarchists.

2274
02:25:40,941 --> 02:25:43,023
Wherever the first firebomb
is thrown,

2275
02:25:43,026 --> 02:25:45,313
wherever the first
brick is thrown,

2276
02:25:45,320 --> 02:25:48,108
wherever the first house
is set on fire,

2277
02:25:48,114 --> 02:25:50,606
then we will make our move.

2278
02:25:50,617 --> 02:25:52,824
I have been in contact
with Washington

2279
02:25:52,827 --> 02:25:56,161
and have been promised
full support.

2280
02:25:56,164 --> 02:25:59,452
Well, so much for any hope
of getting the federal marshals.

2281
02:25:59,459 --> 02:26:00,995
And to every citizen
in this state,

2282
02:26:01,002 --> 02:26:04,040
let me be perfectly clear.

2283
02:26:04,047 --> 02:26:06,288
We will move with everything
in our power

2284
02:26:06,299 --> 02:26:08,711
to protect all life--

2285
02:26:08,718 --> 02:26:11,005
Oh, no. Would you believe it?

2286
02:26:11,012 --> 02:26:11,968
Look at that.

2287
02:26:11,972 --> 02:26:13,462
This has been
a remote telecast

2288
02:26:13,473 --> 02:26:15,214
direct from the governor's
office

2289
02:26:15,225 --> 02:26:16,306
at the state capital.

2290
02:26:16,309 --> 02:26:19,222
God above. How can they
be so stupid?

2291
02:26:19,229 --> 02:26:23,314
No, it's not stupid.
It's a well thought-out plan.

2292
02:26:54,222 --> 02:26:55,337
Oh, I almost forgot.

2293
02:26:55,348 --> 02:26:57,259
Call Joe, tell him
I won't be in to work

2294
02:26:57,267 --> 02:26:59,053
k for three or four
more days.

2295
02:26:59,060 --> 02:27:01,427
Please, please be careful.

2296
02:27:01,438 --> 02:27:03,224
Don't worry, for God's sakes.

2297
02:27:03,231 --> 02:27:04,721
Why is Mommy so upset?

2298
02:27:04,733 --> 02:27:07,566
Well, she's just
being silly, Danny.

2299
02:27:07,569 --> 02:27:09,401
Now give your old dad a hug.

2300
02:27:09,404 --> 02:27:10,644
It's gotta last me
a couple days.

2301
02:27:13,742 --> 02:27:15,608
The governor's office
wants verification

2302
02:27:15,618 --> 02:27:17,325
that radicals are pouring
into the school

2303
02:27:17,329 --> 02:27:18,535
from all over the state.

2304
02:27:18,538 --> 02:27:20,529
- Verified.
- Verified.

2305
02:27:25,879 --> 02:27:27,085
All right.

2306
02:27:27,088 --> 02:27:28,920
Now, it's your job to cover
the hill.

2307
02:27:28,923 --> 02:27:32,257
Any kid <i>comes</i> up from the school
you warn him once.

2308
02:27:32,260 --> 02:27:34,922
You fire a warning shot in the
air and then you shoot to kill.

2309
02:27:34,929 --> 02:27:38,092
Now, they've got snipers
all over the place out there.

2310
02:27:38,099 --> 02:27:40,761
Is that clear?
Do you understand that?

2311
02:27:43,605 --> 02:27:46,393
Does he really expect us
to shoot college kids?

2312
02:27:46,399 --> 02:27:48,265
You're damned right.

2313
02:27:48,276 --> 02:27:50,438
Their snipers will hit you
without batting an eye.

2314
02:27:50,445 --> 02:27:53,437
Pardon me for sounding stupid,

2315
02:27:53,448 --> 02:27:55,405
but, uh, what are we
shooting them for?

2316
02:28:20,809 --> 02:28:22,971
The medicine failed.

2317
02:28:22,977 --> 02:28:24,513
Those bullets are killing you.

2318
02:28:36,991 --> 02:28:40,450
Grandfather said it's because
you didn't respect your vision.

2319
02:28:40,453 --> 02:28:44,412
You acted the same way after
as you did before.

2320
02:28:56,261 --> 02:28:59,379
Grandfather is right.

2321
02:28:59,389 --> 02:29:01,505
But we still
have to stop them,

2322
02:29:01,516 --> 02:29:05,350
because they're going
to try to kill Jean.

2323
02:29:11,651 --> 02:29:15,110
Will any of you help me?

2324
02:29:16,239 --> 02:29:19,152
Please. I can't do it alone.

2325
02:29:26,749 --> 02:29:28,285
Ah!

2326
02:29:42,223 --> 02:29:43,463
Let's burn their supply shack.

2327
02:29:51,107 --> 02:29:53,223
Have any of you guys
seen Danny?

2328
02:29:53,234 --> 02:29:55,191
Please, have any
of you seen Danny?

2329
02:29:55,195 --> 02:29:56,902
- No.
- Yeah, I think I saw him

2330
02:29:56,905 --> 02:29:58,691
running back towards
the girls' dorm.

2331
02:29:58,698 --> 02:29:59,529
Thank you

2332
02:30:03,786 --> 02:30:05,368
Has Danny been through here?

2333
02:30:05,371 --> 02:30:06,702
- You mean little Danny?
- Yes.

2334
02:30:06,706 --> 02:30:09,323
Yeah, well, I think I saw him
go down to the bonfire.

2335
02:30:12,587 --> 02:30:13,918
Carol, you can't
go down there.

2336
02:30:13,922 --> 02:30:16,038
I have to.
I have to find Danny.

2337
02:30:16,049 --> 02:30:17,210
Carol, please.

2338
02:30:22,388 --> 02:30:23,970
Now they've set
a shack on fire.

2339
02:30:23,973 --> 02:30:27,386
You better send a fire truck and
more men to push them back.

2340
02:30:27,393 --> 02:30:28,383
Right. Over.

2341
02:30:51,960 --> 02:30:55,123
Form your lines. Form
your lines, gentlemen.

2342
02:30:55,129 --> 02:30:57,291
This is Jean Roberts
at the Freedom School.

2343
02:30:57,298 --> 02:31:00,086
I have urgent information
that can stop all this.

2344
02:31:00,093 --> 02:31:02,255
Tell the governor he's got
to get on the phone now.

2345
02:31:05,932 --> 02:31:07,422
Wasn't that a sniper?

2346
02:31:07,433 --> 02:31:08,844
Sure looks like it.

2347
02:31:08,851 --> 02:31:11,764
Well, why didn't you
fire back?

2348
02:31:11,771 --> 02:31:13,432
I'm not doing anything
until I get my orders.

2349
02:31:13,439 --> 02:31:15,100
Why don't you just go call
an ambulance.

2350
02:31:16,484 --> 02:31:18,646
Governor?

2351
02:31:18,653 --> 02:31:20,815
Yes. Any kind of statement
from you

2352
02:31:20,822 --> 02:31:22,358
will calm things
down considerably.

2353
02:31:24,158 --> 02:31:26,195
Would you please let me go out
and tell them anything?

2354
02:31:26,202 --> 02:31:27,863
Anything direct from you?

2355
02:31:27,870 --> 02:31:30,658
If the students draw back,

2356
02:31:30,665 --> 02:31:32,997
and seal themselves
in the dormitory,

2357
02:31:33,001 --> 02:31:35,459
then I'll pull back
the militia.

2358
02:31:35,461 --> 02:31:38,670
If not, we'll stop this
at all costs.

2359
02:31:38,673 --> 02:31:40,630
Well, you pull back
your militia

2360
02:31:40,633 --> 02:31:41,839
and I'll get the kids inside.

2361
02:31:41,843 --> 02:31:44,005
God above, at least
give me that chance.

2362
02:31:54,814 --> 02:31:57,021
- Have you seen Danny?
- No, I've been with Joanne.

2363
02:31:57,025 --> 02:31:59,062
Try the playground,
I'll try the barn.

2364
02:31:59,068 --> 02:32:00,979
He's probably
down with his burro.

2365
02:32:02,572 --> 02:32:04,404
General, there is a sniper.

2366
02:32:04,407 --> 02:32:06,489
Lieutenant Stowe, take
your squad around the hill

2367
02:32:06,492 --> 02:32:08,028
to the other side of that wall

2368
02:32:08,036 --> 02:32:09,367
and see if you can find
that sniper.

2369
02:32:09,370 --> 02:32:09,950
Yes, sir.

2370
02:32:09,954 --> 02:32:11,536
What kind of buck shot
are you using?

2371
02:32:11,539 --> 02:32:12,199
Double ought.

2372
02:32:12,206 --> 02:32:14,072
That's equivalent
to a .38 caliber, sir.

2373
02:32:14,083 --> 02:32:16,370
I know what it's equivalent
to but if it will kill a deer,

2374
02:32:16,377 --> 02:32:17,583
it will kill those bastards.

2375
02:32:27,555 --> 02:32:32,220
Sieg Heil! Sieg Heil!

2376
02:32:49,702 --> 02:32:51,192
Hendrick, fire a warning shot.

2377
02:32:52,872 --> 02:32:54,829
What the hell was that?

2378
02:32:57,251 --> 02:32:59,993
The sniper, he's firing at us.

2379
02:33:05,843 --> 02:33:07,254
God, they're
really shooting at us.

2380
02:33:07,261 --> 02:33:09,548
This is Sergeant Tibbs
at the north wall.

2381
02:33:09,555 --> 02:33:11,137
<i>Being fired on by a sniper.</i>

2382
02:33:11,140 --> 02:33:12,471
<i>One man's been hit. Over.</i>

2383
02:33:12,475 --> 02:33:14,057
They're firing
on all sides, sir.

2384
02:33:14,060 --> 02:33:16,392
Damn it to hell, return fire.

2385
02:33:16,396 --> 02:33:18,854
All state troopers.
Fire at will.

2386
02:34:03,985 --> 02:34:07,273
Danny?

2387
02:34:16,456 --> 02:34:21,951
Stop it. Stop it.
Stop it.

2388
02:34:21,961 --> 02:34:24,419
Stop it!

2389
02:34:31,637 --> 02:34:32,843
Carol.

2390
02:34:32,847 --> 02:34:35,680
What the hell
are you waiting for?

2391
02:34:35,683 --> 02:34:38,345
Come on, move it.

2392
02:34:39,771 --> 02:34:41,353
Not in the damn air, mister.

2393
02:34:41,355 --> 02:34:44,438
Down into the crowd. Now.

2394
02:34:46,569 --> 02:34:47,183
Carol?

2395
02:34:58,998 --> 02:35:03,162
Danny? Danny?

2396
02:35:27,276 --> 02:35:30,519
Please someone help me!

2397
02:35:36,202 --> 02:35:37,818
Please help!

2398
02:35:51,634 --> 02:35:52,874
What the hell?

2399
02:35:59,183 --> 02:36:01,174
Colonel, what's going on
down there?

2400
02:36:03,938 --> 02:36:07,681
Help me!

2401
02:37:04,749 --> 02:37:06,990
Under authority
of the Treaty of 1868,

2402
02:37:07,001 --> 02:37:10,414
I am arresting you for being
illegally on Indian land.

2403
02:37:11,505 --> 02:37:14,293
If you resist, or if you
want to continue

2404
02:37:14,300 --> 02:37:16,962
this senseless slaughter
of these unarmed students

2405
02:37:16,969 --> 02:37:20,132
who are here
under our protection,

2406
02:37:20,139 --> 02:37:22,301
then you'll have to shoot
your way through us.

2407
02:37:22,308 --> 02:37:24,891
This is a monumental step
you're taking.

2408
02:37:24,894 --> 02:37:27,886
You give us no other choice.

2409
02:37:27,897 --> 02:37:31,982
If this country must have
another civil war,

2410
02:37:31,984 --> 02:37:33,816
then let it start here.

2411
02:37:33,819 --> 02:37:36,311
What the hell is he doing?

2412
02:38:27,415 --> 02:38:29,076
All right.

2413
02:38:29,083 --> 02:38:30,869
I'll notify the governor.

2414
02:38:38,884 --> 02:38:41,501
Somebody help us, please.

2415
02:38:50,938 --> 02:38:52,599
No, we're pulling out.

2416
02:38:52,606 --> 02:38:55,394
You should have been here
tonight, old buddy.

2417
02:38:55,401 --> 02:38:56,891
We got a couple of them.

2418
02:39:13,377 --> 02:39:16,119
It's funny.

2419
02:39:16,130 --> 02:39:18,462
I thought the Freedom School

2420
02:39:18,466 --> 02:39:22,300
was a symbol of everything
good and right

2421
02:39:22,303 --> 02:39:24,214
in the American spirit.

2422
02:39:27,850 --> 02:39:32,811
We had kids
of different races,

2423
02:39:32,813 --> 02:39:36,306
ideologies, religions,

2424
02:39:36,317 --> 02:39:39,560
all living and working
together in peace and harmony.

2425
02:39:47,578 --> 02:39:49,615
For all the kids
at the school,

2426
02:39:49,622 --> 02:39:51,784
we really want you back.

2427
02:39:54,126 --> 02:39:55,742
Aren't you going to
open it again?

2428
02:39:57,797 --> 02:40:01,540
It's not the kids.

2429
02:40:01,550 --> 02:40:03,837
It's the townspeople.

2430
02:40:03,844 --> 02:40:06,962
They not only supported
the shooting,

2431
02:40:06,972 --> 02:40:09,134
but if you can believe it,

2432
02:40:09,141 --> 02:40:11,633
they were actually happy
about it.

2433
02:40:34,458 --> 02:40:35,823
What do they think?

2434
02:40:35,835 --> 02:40:37,246
Will he come back
or is he dead yet?

2435
02:40:37,253 --> 02:40:40,041
No, not yet.

2436
02:40:40,047 --> 02:40:43,210
Some of the old men say that
he's lost the will to live.

2437
02:40:43,217 --> 02:40:45,128
Go see if you can find Jean
and get her up here.

2438
02:40:58,566 --> 02:40:59,681
You have not learned enough

2439
02:40:59,692 --> 02:41:01,774
to come over
to this side permanently.

2440
02:41:01,986 --> 02:41:05,274
Why? My spirit progresses
so poorly on the other side.

2441
02:41:06,157 --> 02:41:08,364
That's because you don't value
your visions.

2442
02:41:08,367 --> 02:41:11,075
You must carefully listen
to them and change your life

2443
02:41:11,078 --> 02:41:13,365
according to what they say.

2444
02:41:13,372 --> 02:41:15,238
I understand that.

2445
02:41:15,249 --> 02:41:16,990
But why can't I do that here?

2446
02:41:17,168 --> 02:41:20,411
You must go back, for when
people can see how someone

2447
02:41:20,421 --> 02:41:24,255
as violent as you can change
and find inner peace,

2448
02:41:24,258 --> 02:41:26,716
then you will set
a good example.

2449
02:41:26,719 --> 02:41:29,928
After you have gone back
and practiced the fourth way,

2450
02:41:30,139 --> 02:41:32,471
then you will meet
your spiritual guide.

2451
02:41:32,474 --> 02:41:34,385
Well, how am I supposed
to do that?

2452
02:41:34,393 --> 02:41:36,760
I don't even know
what the fourth way is.

2453
02:41:36,770 --> 02:41:38,636
My friend will tell you.

2454
02:41:38,647 --> 02:41:41,435
But you will not be able
to reach the fourth way

2455
02:41:41,442 --> 02:41:43,809
until you stop covering
your weaknesses

2456
02:41:43,819 --> 02:41:45,605
with violent acts.

2457
02:41:45,613 --> 02:41:47,604
The fourth and highest level
is when,

2458
02:41:47,615 --> 02:41:49,322
no matter what
they do to your body

2459
02:41:49,325 --> 02:41:51,692
they cannot touch your soul,

2460
02:41:51,702 --> 02:41:53,989
because you are so deeply
into your own center.

2461
02:41:53,996 --> 02:41:56,033
Then you see violence
and anger

2462
02:41:56,040 --> 02:41:57,906
and bullying
not as threats,

2463
02:41:57,917 --> 02:42:00,204
but as cover-ups used
